00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Welcome to the widget engineering lecture.

2
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:15,000
Today we cover the three laws of widget dynamics.

3
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:20,000
The first law states that a widget at rest stays at rest.

4
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:50,000
The second law relates torque to spin acceleration.

5
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:40,000
Remember: the exam covers laws one and two only.

6
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:30,000
Finally, error code E42 means the widget cache is stale.
